      • isSuccessful

        public boolean isSuccessful()
        Was the validation successful (in other words, do we have no issues that are at severity ResultSeverityEnum.ERROR or ResultSeverityEnum.FATAL. A validation is still considered successful if it only has issues at level ResultSeverityEnum.WARNING or lower.
        Returns:
        true if the validation was successful
